{"tid":2497120,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"首宗「回港易」確診   張竹君：料本地確診","createTime":"2021-04-20T09:49:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T11:18:27.000Z","uid":1251,"like":70,"dislike":251,"uniUserReply":103,"replies":[{"pid":"923550feff685c2ee478fee95f30673161eea446","tid":2497120,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T09:49:35.000Z","msg":"首宗「回港易」確診    內地回港婦人曾做如心酒店房務員   <br />\n同事住客須檢疫   張竹君：料本地確診<br />\n<br />\n本港武漢肺炎疫情轉向緩和，政府早前宣布擴大免檢疫「回港易」計劃，讓內地港人免疫苗回港，但今日出現首宗經「回港易」返港後確診的個案。<br />\n<br />\n病人是一名 46 歲女子，她回港後不需隔離，期間曾到荃灣如心酒店做房務員和到多處用膳。衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君指出，患者由 4 月 6 日到港後有較長活動時間，認為是本地感染機會較大。<br />\n<br />\n記者會直播：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3n1dSdz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3n1dSdz&d=aLufatioEIfsHY%2FyaDEQJwp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=57f94076\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3n1dSdz</a>"},{"pid":"13cc7e2d57012099f53814d3e900f727924f6cb3","tid":2497120,"uid":1251,"like":305,"dislike":2,"score":303,"citedBy":13,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T09:50:16.000Z","msg":"21日就海外感染未病發<br />\n十幾日就香港感染<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ff47d0f1dbc4f934afde18dcc5825dae7b71a35","tid":2497120,"uid":9193,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"13cc7e2d57012099f53814d3e900f727924f6cb3","tid":2497120,"uid":1251,"like":305,"dislike":2,"score":303,"citedBy":13,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T09:50:16.000Z","msg":"21日就海外感染未病發<br />\n十幾日就香港感染<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T09:50:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b144762c44df62ee300bbd95168071af0739ce54","tid":2497120,"uid":1251,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T09:52:27.000Z","msg":"香港咁危險就唔好開放俾同胞落黎啦<br />\n係咪想危害同胞安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":